    "locale": "en",
    "id": "ai-skill-learning",
    "content": "# AI Skill Learning: From Zero to Real Output\n**Learn AI by building one small thing that actually works.**\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start\nYou watch AI tutorials, but you still can’t build anything. This playbook turns learning into output.\n\n---\n\n## Who It’s For\nProfessionals and creators who want AI skills that show up in real work (prompting, automation, agents).\n\n---\n\n## The Pain (Tutorials without output)\n- You consume content but don’t produce results.\n- You don’t know what project to build first.\n- You lack a repeatable learning loop.\n\n---\n\n## The Simple Learning Logic\n- **Project‑based learning:** Skills stick when you ship something.\n- **Micro‑feedback loops:** Small iterations beat big vague plans.\n\n---\n\n## The Human‑Agent Split\n**Agent does**\n- Breaks a project into small tasks.\n- Finds examples and suggests tooling.\n- Reviews outputs and proposes fixes.\n\n**Human does**\n- Chooses the project scope.\n- Makes key product decisions.\n- Polishes the final output.\n\n---\n\n## The 3‑Step Routine (20 min/day)\n**1) Scope (3 min)**\nPick one micro‑project (e.g., summarize emails, create a Q&A bot, automate research notes).\n\n**2) Build (12 min)**\nFollow the agent’s step‑by‑step tasks and produce a working version.\n\n**3) Ship (5 min)**\nSave the output and write one improvement for tomorrow.\n\n---\n\n## Expected Outcomes (Time‑boxed)\n- **7 days:** one working AI mini‑tool.\n- **14 days:** a repeatable build workflow.\n- **30 days:** 2–3 AI projects you can showcase.\n\n---\n\n## Starter Prompt (Example, Unverified)\nUse this once to generate today’s workflow:\n\n```\nBreak down this AI mini‑project into 3 executable steps: \nProject: auto‑summarize meeting notes into 5 action items.\nGive step 1 in detail.\n```\n\n---\n\n## Skill Pack\n\n**Candidate Skills (not yet verified)**\n- Prompt Workflow Builder: https://skills.sh/search?q=prompt%20workflow\n- Agent Task Decomposer: https://skills.sh/search?q=task%20decomposition\n- Tool Finder: https://skills.sh/search?q=tool%20discovery\n- Output Critique Coach: https://skills.sh/search?q=review%20assistant\n\n**Verified Skills (downloadable)**\n- Summarize (URLs/files/videos): https://skills.sh/moltbot/moltbot/summarize\n- AI Learning Studio: https://skills.sh/cantino/claude-skills/ai-learning-studio\n- Prompt Workflow Builder: https://skills.sh/noraj/claude-skills/prompt-workflow-builder\n\n---\n\n## Evidence & Verification\n- **UNTESTED**: Not yet validated by humans\n- **TESTED**: 2+ users × 3 days\n- **VERIFIED**: 10+ users × 7 days\n\n**Current status:** UNTESTED\n\nIf you test this, report your results and we’ll upgrade the status.\n\n---\n\n## Call to Action\nPick the smallest project you can finish this week—and finish it.\n---\n\n## Open‑Source Community\nThis playbook is community‑maintained. If you improve it, share your changes so others benefit.\n\n**Contribute**\n- Improve clarity or add better scenarios\n- Add a real downloadable skill (link + repo)\n- Report test results (what you tried, for how long, and the outcome)\n\n\n\n---\n\n## Change Log\n- 2026‑02‑07 (UTC): Added open‑source contribution sections.\n"
