    "id": "career-learning-loop",
    "content": "# Career Learning Loop: Grow While You Work\n**Turn real work problems into a learning engine.**\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start\nYou’re busy, but you want to level up. This playbook ties learning directly to your job.\n\n---\n\n## Who It’s For\nProfessionals who want measurable growth without leaving their work context.\n\n---\n\n## The Pain (Growth feels disconnected)\n- Learning feels detached from real tasks.\n- You don’t know what skills matter most right now.\n- Growth feels slow and invisible.\n\n---\n\n## The Simple Learning Logic\n- **Learn from real problems.**\n- **Apply immediately to lock in skill gains.**\n\n---\n\n## The Human‑Agent Split\n**Agent does**\n- Extracts learning goals from your tasks.\n- Builds micro‑lessons tied to real work.\n- Tracks progress and suggests next moves.\n\n**Human does**\n- Chooses the priority skill.\n- Applies it in real work.\n- Reflects on impact.\n\n---\n\n## The 3‑Step Routine (20 min/day)\n**1) Identify (3 min)**\nPick one work task you struggled with this week.\n\n**2) Learn (12 min)**\nThe agent generates a focused lesson or checklist.\n\n**3) Apply (5 min)**\nUse it in your next task and record the result.\n\n---\n\n## Expected Outcomes (Time‑boxed)\n- **7 days:** clarity on your top 1 skill gap.\n- **14 days:** visible improvement in one work task.\n- **30 days:** measurable growth in your role.\n\n---\n\n## Starter Prompt (Example, Unverified)\nUse this once to generate today’s workflow:\n\n```\nFrom this week’s hardest work task, extract 1 skill gap and 3 training actions I can do in 20 minutes.\n```\n\n---\n\n## Skill Pack\n\n**Candidate Skills (not yet verified)**\n- Work Task Analyzer: https://skills.sh/search?q=task%20analysis\n- Skill Gap Detector: https://skills.sh/search?q=skill%20gap\n- Micro‑Lesson Builder: https://skills.sh/search?q=lesson%20builder\n- Progress Tracker: https://skills.sh/search?q=progress%20tracker\n\n**Verified Skills (downloadable)**\n\n\n\n- Finding Mentors & Sponsors: https://skills.sh/refoundai/lenny-skills/finding-mentors-sponsors\n- oya (goal planning + coaching prompts): https://skills.sh/foogunlana/skills/oya\n- Career Transitions: https://skills.sh/refoundai/lenny-skills/career-transitions\n- Having Difficult Conversations: https://skills.sh/refoundai/lenny-skills/having-difficult-conversations\n- Team Rituals: https://skills.sh/refoundai/lenny-skills/team-rituals\n- Meeting Insights Analyzer: https://skills.sh/composiohq/awesome-claude-skills/meeting-insights-analyzer\n- Workshop Facilitator: https://skills.sh/eddiebe147/claude-settings/workshop-facilitator\n- Personal Strategic Planning: https://skills.sh/krishagel/geoffrey/personal-strategic-planning\n\n- Requesting Code Review: https://skills.sh/obra/superpowers/requesting-code-review\n- Code Reviewer: https://skills.sh/google-gemini/gemini-cli/code-reviewer\n- Frontend Code Review: https://skills.sh/langgenius/dify/frontend-code-review\n- Continuous Learning v2: https://skills.sh/affaan-m/everything-claude-code/continuous-learning-v2\n\n- Receiving Code Review: https://skills.sh/obra/superpowers/receiving-code-review\n- Code Review Excellence: https://skills.sh/wshobson/agents/code-review-excellence\n\n---\n\n## Evidence & Verification\n- **UNTESTED**: Not yet validated by humans\n- **TESTED**: 2+ users × 3 days\n- **VERIFIED**: 10+ users × 7 days\n\n**Current status:** UNTESTED\n\nIf you test this, report your results and we’ll upgrade the status.\n\n---\n\n## Call to Action\nPick one hard task this week and turn it into your learning trigger.\n---\n\n## Open‑Source Community\nThis playbook is community‑maintained. If you improve it, share your changes so others benefit.\n\n**Contribute**\n- Improve clarity or add better scenarios\n- Add a real downloadable skill (link + repo)\n- Report test results (what you tried, for how long, and the outcome)\n\n\n\n---\n\n## Change Log\n- 2026‑02‑07 (UTC): Added open‑source contribution sections."
