    "locale": "en",
    "id": "crypto-kol-operations",
    "content": "# Crypto KOL Operations: Build Influence in Web3\n**Grow a real audience, not just follower counts.**\n\n> **Disclaimer:** This playbook is for educational purposes only. Always disclose paid promotions and sponsorships. Promoting tokens without disclosure may violate regulations in your jurisdiction.\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start\nYou want to become a crypto KOL, but your tweets get zero engagement. This playbook builds a systematic content and community growth engine for Web3.\n\n---\n\n## Who It's For\nAspiring and early‑stage crypto KOLs, project marketers, and community managers who want to build genuine influence in the Web3 space.\n\n---\n\n## The Pain (Posting into the void)\n- You tweet daily but nobody engages.\n- You don't know what content resonates with crypto audiences.\n- You have no system for tracking what works and doubling down.\n\n---\n\n## The Simple Learning Logic\n- **Value first, followers second:** People follow accounts that make them smarter or richer. Pick one.\n- **Consistency compounds:** One viral tweet is luck. Posting useful content daily for 90 days is a strategy.\n\n---\n\n## The Human‑Agent Split\n**Agent does**\n- Analyzes top‑performing crypto KOL accounts for content patterns (format, timing, topics).\n- Generates content ideas based on trending on‑chain events and market narratives.\n- Tracks engagement metrics and identifies which content types drive growth.\n\n**Human does**\n- Defines their unique angle and persona (alpha caller, educator, analyst, meme lord).\n- Writes or refines the final content with authentic voice.\n- Engages directly with followers and builds real relationships.\n\n---\n\n## The 4‑Step Routine (25 min/day)\n**1) Trend Scan (5 min)**\nReview the agent's daily brief: top trending tokens, on‑chain events, breaking news, and what top KOLs are talking about.\n\n**2) Content Draft (10 min)**\nThe agent proposes 3 tweet ideas based on trends and your persona. Pick one, refine it, add your unique take.\n\n**3) Engage (7 min)**\nReply to 5 relevant tweets from bigger accounts. The agent suggests high‑visibility threads to join. Add genuine insight, not \"gm.\"\n\n**4) Metrics Review (3 min)**\nCheck this week's numbers: impressions, engagement rate, follower growth, best‑performing tweet. The agent highlights what to repeat.\n\n---\n\n## Expected Outcomes (Time‑boxed)\n- **7 days:** a defined persona and content calendar for the first month.\n- **14 days:** 10+ published tweets with tracked engagement metrics.\n- **30 days:** measurable follower growth and 2–3 tweets that outperformed your average by 3x.\n\n---\n\n## Starter Prompt (Example, Unverified)\nUse this once to generate today's workflow:\n\n```\nAnalyze the top 5 crypto KOLs on Twitter by engagement rate this week.\nFor each: top tweet, format used (thread/meme/alpha call/chart), topic, engagement metrics.\nBased on my persona (on-chain analyst), suggest 3 tweet ideas I can post today.\nInclude a hook, body structure, and call-to-action for each.\n```\n\n---\n\n## Skill Pack\n\n**Candidate Skills (not yet verified)**\n- KOL Analytics Engine: https://skills.sh/search?q=kol%20analytics\n- Content Calendar Generator: https://skills.sh/search?q=content%20calendar\n- Engagement Optimizer: https://skills.sh/search?q=engagement%20optimization\n- Trend Aggregator: https://skills.sh/search?q=crypto%20trend%20aggregator\n\n**Verified Skills (downloadable)**\n- @lobster-u/kol-manager: https://skills.sh/lobster-u/kol-manager\n\n---\n\n## Evidence & Verification\n- **UNTESTED**: Not yet validated by humans\n- **TESTED**: 2+ users × 3 days\n- **VERIFIED**: 10+ users × 7 days\n\n**Current status:** UNTESTED\n\nIf you test this, report your results and we'll upgrade the status.\n\n---\n\n## Call to Action\nDefine your KOL persona in one sentence. Then write one tweet today that only you could write.\n\n---\n\n## Open‑Source Community\nThis playbook is community‑maintained. If you improve it, share your changes so others benefit.\n\n**Contribute**\n- Improve clarity or add better scenarios\n- Add a real downloadable skill (link + repo)\n- Report test results (what you tried, for how long, and the outcome)\n\n---\n\n## Change Log\n- 2026‑03‑09 (UTC): Initial version.\n"
