    "locale": "en",
    "id": "micro-learning-daily-digest",
    "content": "# Micro‑Learning Daily Digest: Learn in 5 Minutes\n**A tiny daily routine that compounds without burning you out.**\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start\nYou don’t need more time. You need a system that works in the time you already have.\n\n---\n\n## Who It’s For\nBusy professionals who want steady learning progress without long study sessions.\n\n---\n\n## The Pain (No time to learn)\n- You want to learn, but you’re always busy.\n- Big courses feel impossible to start.\n- You forget what you learned yesterday.\n\n---\n\n## The Simple Learning Logic\n- **Tiny daily effort beats occasional big effort.**\n- **Consistency creates momentum.**\n\n---\n\n## The Human‑Agent Split\n**Agent does**\n- Generates a daily 5‑minute lesson.\n- Sends a micro‑quiz or prompt.\n- Tracks streaks and adjustments.\n\n**Human does**\n- Shows up daily.\n- Answers the prompt.\n- Reflects on one takeaway.\n\n---\n\n## The 3‑Step Routine (5–10 min/day)\n**1) Read (2 min)**\nConsume a small piece of high‑signal content.\n\n**2) Respond (5 min)**\nAnswer a quick question or mini‑quiz.\n\n**3) Save (2 min)**\nWrite one sentence you want to remember.\n\n---\n\n## Expected Outcomes (Time‑boxed)\n- **7 days:** a consistent learning streak.\n- **14 days:** noticeable recall improvement.\n- **30 days:** one new usable skill or concept.\n\n---\n\n## Starter Prompt (Example, Unverified)\nUse this once to generate today’s workflow:\n\n```\nGenerate today’s 5‑minute learning digest on prompt engineering basics with 1 quick quiz question.\n```\n\n---\n\n## Skill Pack\n\n**Candidate Skills (not yet verified)**\n- Daily Digest Generator: https://skills.sh/search?q=daily%20digest\n- Micro‑Quiz Builder: https://skills.sh/search?q=quiz\n- Streak Tracker: https://skills.sh/search?q=habit%20tracker\n- Flashcard Maker: https://skills.sh/search?q=flashcards\n\n**Verified Skills (downloadable)**\n- Summarize (URLs/files/videos): https://skills.sh/moltbot/moltbot/summarize\n- RemNote: https://skills.sh/andrejones92/canifi-life-os/remnote\n- Memory, Retrieval & Learning: https://agent-skills.md/skills/lyndonkl/claude/memory-retrieval-learning\n- Flashcard Maker: https://skills.sh/agentic-ai/skills/flashcard-maker\n\n---\n\n## Evidence & Verification\n- **UNTESTED**: Not yet validated by humans\n- **TESTED**: 2+ users × 3 days\n- **VERIFIED**: 10+ users × 7 days\n\n**Current status:** UNTESTED\n\nIf you test this, report your results and we’ll upgrade the status.\n\n---\n\n## Call to Action\nStart tomorrow morning: one page, one question, one sentence.\n---\n\n## Open‑Source Community\nThis playbook is community‑maintained. If you improve it, share your changes so others benefit.\n\n**Contribute**\n- Improve clarity or add better scenarios\n- Add a real downloadable skill (link + repo)\n- Report test results (what you tried, for how long, and the outcome)\n\n\n\n---\n\n## Change Log\n- 2026‑02‑07 (UTC): Added open‑source contribution sections.\n"
